reeLabelNs14 CategoryTreeLabelCategory" href="/wiki/Category:Works_based_on_the_Book_of_Mormon">Works based on the Book of Mormon</a></div>\n<div class="CategoryTreeChildren" style="display:none"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="CategoryTreeSection">\n<div class="CategoryTreeItem"><span class="CategoryTreeEmptyBullet">\xe2\x96\xba</span> <a class="CategoryTreeLabel  CategoryTreeLabelNs14 CategoryTreeLabelCategory" href="/wiki/Category:Book_of_Mormon_portal">Book of Mormon portal</a></div>\n<div class="CategoryTreeChildren" style="display:none"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="noprint" style="margin:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em; padding:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em; text-align:right;"></div>\n<div style="clear:both;"></div>\n</div>\n<p><br /></p>\n</div>\n<div style="float:right; width:100%">\n<div style="clear: both; border: solid #aaaaaa; border-width: 1px 1px 0; background: #FFD700; color: black; padding: .1em;padding-top: .1em;padding-left: .1em;padding-right: .1em;padding-bottom: .1em;text-align: center;font-family: sans-serif;font-size:100%;margin-bottom: 0px;">\n<div class="plainlinks" style="float:right;margin-bottom:.1em;font-size:80%; color: black"><a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Portal:Book_of_Mormon/Book_of_Mormon_topics&amp;action=edit"><span style="color: black">edit</span></a>&#160;&#160;</div>\n<h2 style="font-family:sans-serif; font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:black;"><span class="mw-headline" id="Topics">Topics</span></h2>\n</div>\n<div style="border: 1px solid #aaaaaa; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: #f9f9ff;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">\n<div style="font-size: 91%; text-align:center;">\n<p><b><a href="/wiki/Book_of_Mormon" title="Book of Mormon">Book of Mormon</a></b>: <a href="/wiki/Book_of_Mormon_chronology" title="Book of Mormon chronology">Book of Mormon